<li class='cover' id='bookCover_7979'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7979.The_Bellmaker"><img alt="The Bellmaker (Redwall, #7)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1386921177l/7979._SX98_.jpg" />
</a>


<script>
